{"tid":197610,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"道德撚，你老母比狗屌呀！","createTime":"2017-04-12T03:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T08:11:59.000Z","uid":5190,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e13ec005299ec005bc4a65182d54cfc73ce2fa","tid":197610,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"先唔講條女比車撞死係咪好抵死<br />\n你地一味叫人積口德有撚用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪都死左架啦 我鍾意點講你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且條女係抵死 依樣係鐵一般嘅事實<br />\n你班道德撚就收皮啦 香港每年發生幾千單意外 你就淨係在意依單？人地非洲每日餓死幾百人呀 又唔見你捐撚晒啲錢去非洲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一味講道德有幾撚重要 屌你啦 道德可以當飯食呀？道德可以當錢洗呀？你唔叫你老細可憐下你比多一個月糧你 等佢可以積返啲陰德？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n積埋積埋攞黎做乜鳩呀？傻仔 比你班道德撚有個籍口先有「陰德」「口德」依個term咋 你以為真係有得積呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咁撚有道德呀 快撚啲捐撚晒你啲衫褲比啲乞衣 捐撚埋你啲血比人啦 道德撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff52e7b8c0bb03356a797b93823386d1c136142","tid":197610,"uid":15895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"辯駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79eb64b3ac72f39f8d603db79bb3456ab95d0bb4","tid":197610,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T07:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辯駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f80b70c27a5309e8d5c26192c9a9173fe6ec7ad","tid":197610,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870756